57
00:03:48,643 --> 00:03:50,603
ルポンは

58
00:03:50,603 --> 00:03:55,023
彼は戦士たちに呼びかけられ、私を捕まえますかと考えました

59
00:03:55,023 --> 00:03:57,783
でもホームズは何も言いませんでした

60
00:03:58,611 --> 00:04:06,311
It took a while for the last man to pass, and when he did, both men looked into each other's eyes.

61
00:04:06,311 --> 00:04:09,211
It was an interesting sight.

62
00:04:09,211 --> 00:04:16,511
The first meeting of two incredible men was so strange and so powerful.

63
00:04:16,511 --> 00:04:20,011
The Englishman was the first to speak.

64
00:04:20,011 --> 00:04:22,211
Thank you, sir.

65
00:04:22,211 --> 00:04:25,671
You are quite welcome, replied Lupin.

66
